🧩 KEY CONCEPTS YOU SHOULD REMEMBER
1. Schema = Structure

Defines how data looks in DB

2. Model = Tool

Used to interact with database

3. Controller = Logic

Handles request & response

4. req (request)

Data coming from frontend

5. res (response)

Data going to frontend

6. API Connection

Frontend → fetch() → Backend → DB → Response → Frontend